The paper deals with the security of cloud-based systems, which is a major concern in the field of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also uses game theory to model the interaction between the cloud, the attacker, and the device, which falls under the category of game theory (cs.GT). The paper also deals with cyber-physical systems, which are systems that integrate physical and cyber components, and control theory, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also uses advanced computational processes, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with unmanned vehicles, which are related to networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
